Recruiting Alert!
Scammers are posing as health care recruiters in an attempt to solicit personal and financial information from candidates. If you suspect you are receiving fraudulent communication regarding a Halyard job posting, please let us know!  Halyard recruiting only uses an ‘@hyh.com’ email address for communicating with candidates, and does not conduct online-only interviews.  Concerned? Confirm recruiting efforts by emailing recruiting.support@hyh.com. Please don’t hesitate to reach out!















